Intro:
	OIC is an onlime image proccessing facility for PHP compatible web servers. This will allow users to 
upload a picture to the server and have it processed into another format.


Requirements:
	PHP 4+ and compatible web Server
	GD
	
Install:
	Place all your files into your web directory and 'chown' the files to the user and group of the web server.

	Example: chown -R nobody.nobody OIC/

	Edit "config.php" with your correct web server and script settings



